Aries is the Zodiac sign of people born between March 21 and April 20. Aries is the first sun sign of the astrological year.
Taurus is the Zodiac sign of people born between April 21 and May 21.
Gemini is the Zodiac sign of people born between May 21 and June 21.
Leo is the Zodiac sign of people born between July 23 and August 21.
Virgo is the Zodiac sign of people born between August 22nd September 23.
Libra is the Zodiac sign of people born between September 24 and October 23.
Scorpio is the Zodiac sign of people born between October 24 and November 22.
Sagittarius is the Zodiac sign of people born between November 23 and December 22.
Aquarius is the Zodiac sign of people born between January 21 and February 19.
Pisces is the Zodiac sign of people born between February 20 and March 20.
